title: Coronavirus: Italy Sees Worst Day Yet; 969 Dead in 24 Hours, Death Toll Exceeds 9,000
description: Italy has hit its highest daily coronavirus death toll yet; 969 people have died in the last 24 hours alone, bringing the nation's overall death toll from the virus to 9,134 as of Friday — an increase of 11.9 percent in one day.
